These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, lemonade, soy-milk
There are 3 different nationalities: indonesian, pakistani, mexican
1. the pakistani is the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is between the mexican and the person drinking lemonade##2
3. the person drinking juice is on the right of the indonesian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3   |
| Beverage      | lemonade | soy-milk | juice |
| Nationality   | pakistani     | indonesian    | mexican   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-2::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, march, february
The people have 3 different jobs:  coach, dressmaker, social-worker
1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
2. the social-worker is between the coach and the person who's birthday is in july##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |       3       |
| Birthday   | july    | february        | march |
| Job     | dressmaker | social-worker | coach         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, mirinda, tea
There 3 different types of food: garlic, pomegranate, eggplant
1. the person eating garlic is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
2. the person drinking cola is between the person eating pomegranate and the person drinking tea##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |  3  |
| Beverage   | mirinda | cola     | tea |
| Food        | pomegranate  | eggplant | garlic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-4::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, r&b, soul
There 3 different types of food: peach, plum, watermelon
1. the fan of funk is the person eating peach##1
2. the fan of soul is between the person eating plum and the person eating peach##2
3. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person eating peach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |
| Music-Genre   | r&b  | soul     | funk |
| Food           | plum | watermelon | peach |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, reading, sudoku
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, country, rock
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the fan of rock##1
3. the fan of funk is between the fan of rock and the fan of country##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3    |
| Hobby   | reading | sudoku     | cooking |
| Music-Genre     | rock    | funk | country    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-6::.
There are 3 different nationalities: dutch, egyptian, indian
The people have 3 different jobs:  engineer, freelancer, photographer
1. the engineer is between the indian and the dutch##2
2. the dutch is the freelancer##1
3. the egyptian is on the right of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |       3       |
| Nationality   | dutch  | egyptian   | indian        |
| Job         | freelancer | engineer | photographer |

