.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-8::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: dancing, magic-tricks, collecting
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, british, mexican
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the mexican##1
2. the british is between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person who's hobby is collecting##2
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |
| Hobby   | collecting   | dancing  | magic-tricks  |
| Nationality   | brazilian | british | mexican |

