.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-9::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: ice-hockey, swimming, weightlifting
The people have 3 different jobs:  photographer, writer, teacher
1. the photographer is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
2. the photographer is between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the writer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3     |
| Sport       | weightlifting | ice-hockey | swimming  |
| Job   | teacher    | photographer        | writer |

