.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-11::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, milk
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, r&b, blues
1. the fan of blues is between the person drinking fanta and the fan of classical##2
2. the person drinking milk is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2     |     3     |
| Beverage   | fanta | 7up      | milk      |
| Music-Genre       | r&b  | blues | classical |

