.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-12::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: reggae, rock, salsa
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, ship, skateboard
1. the fan of rock is on the left of the person driving the car##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is between the person driving the car and the person driving the ship##2
3. the fan of reggae is on the left of the fan of rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | rock   | salsa   |
| Transport         | ship | skateboard | car |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-13::.
3 different pets are kept: ferret, fish, rat
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, swisher, tiparillo
1. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
2. the tiparillo-smoker is between the baccarat-smoker and the owner of the ferret##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |     3     |
| Pet         | ferret | fish  | rat       |
| Cigar   | swisher | tiparillo | baccarat |

 #################################

 
